com.att.aro.model
Class ApplicationSampling

java.lang.Object
  com.att.aro.model.ApplicationSampling

public class ApplicationSampling
extends java.lang.Object

Contains sampled trace analysis data, and provides methods for calculating percentile rankings on that data, for energy, signaling, and throughput.
